1313
00:54:30.739 --> 00:54:32.159
Ovo je. um. Nigel Kittling.

1314
00:54:32.440 --> 00:54:32.940
Nigel.

1315
00:54:33.440 --> 00:54:33.659
Zadovoljstvo mi je.

1316
00:54:34.300 --> 00:54:36.495
A ono je...

1317
00:54:36.519 --> 00:54:37.780
Andy.

1318
00:54:38.320 --> 00:54:38.500
Sash.

1319
00:54:38.840 --> 00:54:39.179
Sash.

1320
00:54:39.380 --> 00:54:39.820
Andy.

1321
00:54:40.119 --> 00:54:41.119
Bok.

1322
00:54:42.099 --> 00:54:43.099
Ta haljina.

1323
00:54:43.139 --> 00:54:44.055
To je...

1324
00:54:44.079 --> 00:54:44.340
Vau.

1325
00:54:44.880 --> 00:54:46.416
Dakle. stvarno...

1326
00:54:46.440 --> 00:54:47.440
Vau.

1327
00:54:48.360 --> 00:54:49.480
Vrlo ugodno.

1328
00:54:49.599 --> 00:54:50.079
Nije visoka moda.

1329
00:54:50.260 --> 00:54:50.699
Nije po mjeri.

1330
00:54:51.079 --> 00:54:52.079
Ali je ugodno.

1331
00:54:52.860 --> 00:54:54.487
Reci mi. ti si cura koja je napisala onaj

1332
00:54:54.511 --> 00:54:56.271
